1
00:00:00,340 --> 00:00:01,710
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,710 --> 00:00:03,410
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,480 --> 00:00:05,280
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:06,380 --> 00:00:07,680
And then there's Driver Song...

5
00:00:08,180 --> 00:00:09,550
(Episode 74)

6
00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:11,920
Your father...

7
00:00:12,250 --> 00:00:15,150
threw a fit
and even flung his tea at me.

8
00:00:17,520 --> 00:00:19,660
You should've seen him
trying to act like a dad.

9
00:00:19,860 --> 00:00:21,290
Who are you calling my dad?

10
00:00:32,070 --> 00:00:35,440
Hyun Jun's not Park Tae Ho's son,

11
00:00:36,470 --> 00:00:38,080
but Driver Song's son?

12
00:00:50,420 --> 00:00:52,660
Is being dramatic genetic?

13
00:00:53,790 --> 00:00:55,490
You two are just alike.

14
00:01:04,870 --> 00:01:06,140
What do you think you're doing?

15
00:01:10,510 --> 00:01:13,510
I was making him pay
for what Driver Song did to me.

16
00:01:15,010 --> 00:01:16,850
Think of it as taking a hit
for your father.

17
00:01:20,220 --> 00:01:24,090
And both of you need to get a grip.

18
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:26,360
It seems you still don't get...

19
00:01:26,420 --> 00:01:28,360
that I have you both
in the palm of my hand.

20
00:01:30,830 --> 00:01:33,870
Don't you think you'll regret
being so stubborn?

21
00:01:34,330 --> 00:01:35,330
Why you...

22
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:39,640
There you go.
Now you're starting to get it.

23
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:44,010
Then you'd better find a way
to take down Park Min Jun,

24
00:01:44,740 --> 00:01:45,810
and fast.

25
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:54,520
Why that... I could just...

26
00:01:58,160 --> 00:01:59,160
Are you okay?

27
00:02:05,330 --> 00:02:07,000
Living
as Chairman Park Tae Ho's son...

28
00:02:08,570 --> 00:02:09,570
is tough.

29
00:02:09,970 --> 00:02:10,970
Hyun Jun.

30
00:02:11,470 --> 00:02:12,900
It's going to keep being this hard,
isn't it?

31
00:02:16,410 --> 00:02:18,940
Every time I have to face
who my father is,

32
00:02:21,950 --> 00:02:23,410
am I going to feel this pathetic?

33
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:26,480
Just hang in there.

34
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:30,320
I've had Chloe looking
for Park Tae Ho's weakness.

35
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:32,220
Once we find it,

36
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,960
we can keep our positions
even if the secret is revealed.

37
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,930
Don't make Chloe do anything shady.

38
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:42,500
- It's nothing shady.
- I...

39
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:50,380
I don't want anyone else
finding out.

40
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:53,610
Not Min Jun, and not Chloe...

41
00:02:55,150 --> 00:02:56,750
Definitely not Chloe.

42
00:02:58,480 --> 00:03:01,250
Please, just let me keep
my last shred of dignity.

43
00:03:02,590 --> 00:03:06,360
Mom, please don't do anything.
Please, don't cause any trouble.

44
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:13,930
Hyun... Hyun Jun.

45
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:15,630
Hyun Jun.

46
00:03:28,850 --> 00:03:31,320
So that's why he didn't
come home that night.

47
00:03:33,380 --> 00:03:36,090
He was so afraid of me finding out,
he couldn't say a word.

48
00:03:37,590 --> 00:03:38,860
He just pretended
like everything was fine.

49
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,400
I'm sorry.

50
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:50,170
What were you so sorry about?

51
00:03:52,700 --> 00:03:55,540
Was it because you weren't
Park Tae Ho's son?

52
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:10,990
What is it?
Why are you looking at me like that?

53
00:04:13,390 --> 00:04:15,090
Your hair, it's wet.

54
00:04:15,830 --> 00:04:18,260
Oh, right. This?

55
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:22,000
I washed my face on my way in.

56
00:04:23,370 --> 00:04:24,540
It's hot out.

57
00:04:26,100 --> 00:04:27,210
Rough, wasn't it?

58
00:04:28,770 --> 00:04:29,770
What?

59
00:04:31,380 --> 00:04:32,380
You just seem...

60
00:04:33,610 --> 00:04:35,110
like you've had a rough day.

61
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,780
I mean, it's hot out.

62
00:04:42,690 --> 00:04:43,690
Right.

63
00:04:46,060 --> 00:04:48,190
I'm going to go meet James.

64
00:04:48,930 --> 00:04:50,260
I might be late.

65
00:04:50,930 --> 00:04:51,930
Should I go with you?

66
00:04:52,300 --> 00:04:54,800
I'd like to help with
what you're working on.

67
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:58,740
It's okay.
I'll let you know if I need help.

68
00:05:05,940 --> 00:05:06,940
Same goes for you.

69
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:11,480
Let me know if you need anything.

70
00:05:27,870 --> 00:05:29,770
I'll never be able to tell you.

71
00:05:33,140 --> 00:05:34,340
Especially not to you.

72
00:05:37,710 --> 00:05:39,310
I can't ever let you find out.

73
00:06:08,740 --> 00:06:11,340
How much longer do I have to wait
for answers about Park Cheol Su?

74
00:06:11,410 --> 00:06:13,680
You said your father
was rich and powerful.

75
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:15,480
So why haven't we heard anything?

76
00:06:16,950 --> 00:06:18,420
How could you...

77
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:21,350
live your life
hiding a secret like that?

78
00:06:21,550 --> 00:06:23,420
Tell him to hurry up.

79
00:06:24,220 --> 00:06:26,120
If this isn't going anywhere,
we need a backup plan,

80
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:28,030
so tell him to get moving.

81
00:06:28,490 --> 00:06:29,860
Are you that nervous?

82
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:31,800
What?

83
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:35,070
You seem nervous and on edge.

84
00:06:36,030 --> 00:06:40,370
If that's how I seem,
take a page from my book...

85
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:41,440
and get it done already.

86
00:06:41,770 --> 00:06:44,080
Also, you can reach Geun Tae, right?

87
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:46,380
Tell him I have a job for him...

88
00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:48,880
and that he needs to come see me
no matter what.

89
00:06:51,420 --> 00:06:53,050
Am I the only one pressed for time?

90
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:00,560
(James)

91
00:07:04,030 --> 00:07:07,330
Yes, it's me.
Any word on Park Cheol Su yet?

92
00:07:10,700 --> 00:07:11,700
Right.

93
00:07:12,570 --> 00:07:13,600
I see.

94
00:07:14,710 --> 00:07:16,110
Yes, I understand.

95
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:19,810
Chairman Park told you
where the slush fund ledger is?

96
00:07:21,210 --> 00:07:25,320
He only told me the location.
It's useless without the key.

97
00:07:26,650 --> 00:07:28,120
He said he'll give me the key...

98
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:30,920
after we register our marriage
and I'm officially his.

99
00:07:31,490 --> 00:07:34,790
Even though I saved his life,
he still doesn't trust me.

100
00:07:35,990 --> 00:07:38,760
He's lived his whole life
being suspicious of everyone.

101
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:41,300
Telling you
where the slush fund ledger is...

102
00:07:41,300 --> 00:07:43,300
and offering you the key...

103
00:07:43,570 --> 00:07:46,140
must've been a difficult decision
for him.

104
00:07:50,370 --> 00:07:51,380
Hey, Woo Jin.

105
00:07:51,980 --> 00:07:52,980
What?

106
00:07:53,780 --> 00:07:55,710
You heard from Eunhwa Trading?

107
00:07:57,720 --> 00:08:01,090
Right. That's great. Okay.

108
00:08:02,190 --> 00:08:04,120
Did Park Cheol Su show up?

109
00:08:04,260 --> 00:08:07,090
They're meeting tomorrow evening
at Eunhwa Trading.

110
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,460
We should tell Jin Ju.

111
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:11,530
He already contacted James,
so she probably heard.

112
00:08:12,530 --> 00:08:15,670
He finally crawled out of the
woodwork, smelling the money.

113
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:20,710
Once we catch Park Cheol Su,
we can uncover the truth...

114
00:08:20,770 --> 00:08:22,740
about Dr. Baek's accident
from seven years ago.

115
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:34,290
What?
Chloe is looking for Park Cheol Su?

116
00:08:34,390 --> 00:08:37,590
Yes, I've been monitoring Chloe
as you instructed,

117
00:08:37,660 --> 00:08:39,760
and I overheard her
on the phone with James.

118
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:42,330
She's looking for Park Cheol Su,

119
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:44,500
but it seems
she hasn't had any luck yet.

120
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:47,370
How did she even find out about him?

121
00:08:47,370 --> 00:08:48,500
At this point,

122
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:52,000
it's safe to assume she learned
about him from Oh Jung Ran.

123
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:56,470
She said she wanted to get
on my good side,

124
00:08:56,470 --> 00:08:58,510
but she's been conspiring
with Oh Jung Ran...

125
00:08:58,510 --> 00:09:00,240
to stab me in the back?

126
00:09:01,010 --> 00:09:04,220
Chloe might
not have lost her memory.

127
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:06,120
If she's still...

128
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:09,190
coming after Adele and me,

129
00:09:09,850 --> 00:09:11,420
I can't just let it slide.

130
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:14,430
Keep an eye on Chloe,

131
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:18,560
and head over to Eunhwa Trading
just to be safe.

132
00:09:18,660 --> 00:09:20,530
Yes, sir.

133
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:21,870
Darn it.

134
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:28,710
When we meet Park Cheol Su,
we can't let him get away.

135
00:09:28,770 --> 00:09:33,140
Yes, that's why I'm posting people
around the building.

136
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:35,610
We'll tail him, catch him,
get a confession,

137
00:09:35,610 --> 00:09:37,150
and then request a reinvestigation.

138
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:39,520
Then Chairman Park's crimes
will be revealed,

139
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:42,520
and Adele Group
will have to find a new owner.

140
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:46,420
Are you still planning
to keep Hyun Jun involved?

141
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:51,630
Actually, there's something
I need to tell you about him.

142
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:57,070
Park Hyun Jun is Driver Song's son?

143
00:09:57,570 --> 00:09:58,570
How on earth...

144
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:03,010
Oh Jung Ran has been living
with a huge secret.

145
00:10:03,540 --> 00:10:06,240
I don't think Hyun Jun found out
that long ago either.

146
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:10,480
Choi Yu Na of all people knows
and is blackmailing him.

147
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:14,420
Talk about a surprise. Wait.

148
00:10:15,190 --> 00:10:16,590
So what happens now?

149
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,660
If he's not Chairman Park's son,

150
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:21,230
does that mean
he can't inherit Adele Group?

151
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:24,000
Does the fact
that he's not Chairman Park's son...

152
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:27,770
actually make him
a better husband for you?

153
00:10:29,230 --> 00:10:30,230
So?

154
00:10:30,970 --> 00:10:32,640
What are you going to do now?

155
00:10:32,970 --> 00:10:36,570
I'll think about what to do about Hyun Jun
as the situation develops.

156
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:39,280
James, you should focus
on Park Cheol Su.

157
00:10:40,380 --> 00:10:42,210
As for me, I have a score...

158
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:44,680
to settle with Choi Yu Na
on Hyun Jun's behalf.

159
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:46,250
With Choi Yu Na?

160
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:49,690
I'm going to show her
how painful it is to suffer...

161
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:52,460
because of a secret.

162
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:08,470
Stop staring and eat, guys.

163
00:11:08,540 --> 00:11:11,040
Like I can get any food down.

164
00:11:12,540 --> 00:11:13,540
Yu Na.

165
00:11:14,110 --> 00:11:15,350
Is it true...

166
00:11:16,180 --> 00:11:17,420
that Park Min Jun
isn't going to sue?

167
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:20,220
How many times do I have to say it?
I told you, he can't.

168
00:11:20,550 --> 00:11:21,550
Actually,

169
00:11:22,220 --> 00:11:24,720
it doesn't matter
even if he does sue me.

170
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:27,160
How can you say it doesn't matter?

171
00:11:27,260 --> 00:11:30,160
I thought we'd be at a disadvantage
if this goes to court.

172
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:34,830
Mom, even if he sues,
it'll take years to get a verdict.

173
00:11:35,300 --> 00:11:37,700
If we hold out until then,
we'll figure something out.

174
00:11:38,570 --> 00:11:41,510
Just holding out
isn't going to solve this.

175
00:11:41,570 --> 00:11:43,710
And what about all the legal fees
we'll be racking up?

176
00:11:43,770 --> 00:11:46,080
That's exactly what I'm saying.

177
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:49,580
What guarantee is there
that you'll win if you hold out?

178
00:11:49,610 --> 00:11:51,120
- There is one.
- What?

179
00:11:52,150 --> 00:11:55,390
There are people
who'll take on Min Jun for me,

180
00:11:55,950 --> 00:11:58,620
- so just wait and see.
- People who will fight for you?

181
00:11:58,620 --> 00:11:59,960
What are you talking about?

182
00:12:05,260 --> 00:12:07,060
A delivery at this hour?

183
00:12:10,170 --> 00:12:11,170
What's this?

184
00:12:19,110 --> 00:12:21,780
What is it? What's going on?

185
00:12:21,980 --> 00:12:23,510
What's this?

186
00:12:24,010 --> 00:12:25,220
What's going on?

187
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:26,920
What is this?

188
00:12:27,150 --> 00:12:31,320
Hold on.
Why does she look so stunned?

189
00:12:31,620 --> 00:12:32,660
Oh, dear.

190
00:12:34,730 --> 00:12:36,830
Wait, is it because of this?

191
00:12:36,860 --> 00:12:39,860
What? It's just a rock.

192
00:12:40,060 --> 00:12:44,440
What kind of sicko would send
something like this? Honestly.

193
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:46,840
It must be some kids
playing a prank.

194
00:12:47,610 --> 00:12:49,010
Look at this.

195
00:12:50,410 --> 00:12:51,610
"Seven years ago..."

196
00:12:51,610 --> 00:12:54,450
"I know what you did
seven years ago."

197
00:12:54,510 --> 00:12:55,580
Seven years ago?

198
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:57,410
Wait, seven years ago?

199
00:12:58,350 --> 00:12:59,580
- What...
- What do I do?

200
00:13:01,020 --> 00:13:03,450
Min Jun mentioned the rock too.

201
00:13:04,220 --> 00:13:07,590
Could he really have found a witness
from that day?

202
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:12,130
Honestly. Who would pull
a prank like this?

203
00:13:12,260 --> 00:13:15,970
People like this won't learn...

204
00:13:16,130 --> 00:13:18,200
until they get hit over the head...

205
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:19,740
with something like this.

206
00:13:20,140 --> 00:13:21,210
Right on the forehead.

207
00:13:21,670 --> 00:13:23,510
Such brats. Goodness.

208
00:13:23,870 --> 00:13:25,880
What... Yu Na, wait!

209
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:29,210
- Where are you going?
- Where's she going with that rock?

210
00:13:34,490 --> 00:13:35,490
It was you, wasn't it?

211
00:13:35,850 --> 00:13:37,520
This was from you, wasn't it?

212
00:13:41,330 --> 00:13:42,430
It's a rock.

213
00:13:43,660 --> 00:13:46,630
You made such a big deal
about me throwing a rock...

214
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:48,000
at Baek Jin Ju.

215
00:13:48,270 --> 00:13:51,070
You sent a similar rock
just to torment me, didn't you?

216
00:13:52,670 --> 00:13:54,140
How did you find out about this?

217
00:13:54,870 --> 00:13:58,310
Are you really
hiding a witness somewhere?

218
00:13:58,810 --> 00:13:59,810
What...

219
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,410
Was it...

220
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:04,380
Jin Ju?

221
00:14:06,050 --> 00:14:07,250
A witness?

222
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:13,760
I came by Hyun Jun's office
and heard you two arguing.

223
00:14:14,060 --> 00:14:16,030
What witness are you talking about?

224
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:22,500
And what's this rock?

225
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:32,380
A rock is a rock.
What else would it be?

226
00:14:35,250 --> 00:14:39,020
Park Min Jun. You can't shake me
with a pathetic prank like this.

227
00:14:39,150 --> 00:14:40,650
In the end,

228
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:44,150
you won't be able to prove a thing,
and I'll be the one who wins.

229
00:14:57,770 --> 00:14:59,000
It was you, wasn't it?

230
00:14:59,740 --> 00:15:00,770
Why did you do it?

231
00:15:01,570 --> 00:15:05,510
Because it seemed like Choi Yu Na
had already forgotten what she did.

232
00:15:05,780 --> 00:15:06,780
Is that all?

233
00:15:07,380 --> 00:15:10,310
She's threatening Hyun Jun
to make you back off.

234
00:15:10,510 --> 00:15:11,520
So,

235
00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:13,780
you stepped in on his behalf?

236
00:15:15,190 --> 00:15:18,160
Choi Yu Na is my problem
to deal with anyway.

237
00:15:20,020 --> 00:15:21,530
I'll get going, then.

238
00:15:25,160 --> 00:15:26,230
- But...
- But...

239
00:15:33,070 --> 00:15:35,970
How did you know
Hyun Jun was being blackmailed?

240
00:15:37,370 --> 00:15:40,480
Don't tell me you also know
why he's being blackmailed.

241
00:15:41,150 --> 00:15:44,180
You know the reason too?

242
00:15:59,760 --> 00:16:00,960
This is for you and Chloe.

243
00:16:01,330 --> 00:16:03,230
Your wedding photo has arrived.

244
00:16:03,230 --> 00:16:05,000
Right. Thank you.

245
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:06,340
I'll let you rest now.

246
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:21,750
A marriage for revenge.

247
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:27,020
If you find out...

248
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:30,630
that I'm not Park Tae Ho's son,

249
00:16:32,930 --> 00:16:34,470
what would you do?

250
00:16:35,470 --> 00:16:36,870
If you went back to Min Jun...

251
00:16:40,570 --> 00:16:42,570
for the sake of your revenge,

252
00:16:45,810 --> 00:16:47,280
where would that leave me?

253
00:16:49,510 --> 00:16:50,510
Could I...

254
00:16:54,750 --> 00:16:56,490
Could I ever let you go?

255
00:17:13,300 --> 00:17:16,140
I have no intention
of using Hyun Jun's secret.

256
00:17:16,570 --> 00:17:18,140
If Hyun Jun needs...

257
00:17:19,180 --> 00:17:21,180
to become the heir
to carry out your revenge,

258
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:25,320
I'll give up and step aside.

259
00:17:26,450 --> 00:17:30,190
What about your mother?
She's counting on you.

260
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:35,090
I'll handle this myself,

261
00:17:35,790 --> 00:17:37,130
so stay out of it.

262
00:17:38,860 --> 00:17:41,060
What's going through your mind?

263
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:45,340
Are you thinking about your revenge,

264
00:17:46,770 --> 00:17:48,840
or about how much
Hyun Jun is suffering?

265
00:17:50,140 --> 00:17:51,340
(Park Tae Ho)

266
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:54,610
She's running late.

267
00:17:56,210 --> 00:17:57,550
Should I go pick her up?

268
00:18:38,620 --> 00:18:40,520
This heartless world.

269
00:18:41,460 --> 00:18:43,490
When has it ever been on my side?

270
00:18:45,930 --> 00:18:46,930
Fine.

271
00:18:47,930 --> 00:18:49,470
Do your worst.

272
00:18:50,570 --> 00:18:52,370
I'll fight tooth and nail...

273
00:18:53,870 --> 00:18:56,410
to protect my son
and take over Adele.

274
00:19:04,010 --> 00:19:05,620
It's not over...

275
00:19:06,980 --> 00:19:08,290
for Oh Jung Ran yet.

276
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:36,950
Our Hyun Jun...

277
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:40,780
Why do you keep saying
"our Hyun Jun?"

278
00:19:48,090 --> 00:19:50,530
No matter how much I call him...

279
00:19:51,260 --> 00:19:52,860
"our Hyun Jun,"

280
00:19:54,770 --> 00:19:55,870
Hyun Jun...

281
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:00,370
is Park Tae Ho's son.

282
00:20:01,910 --> 00:20:03,140
Of course he is.

283
00:20:16,090 --> 00:20:17,150
I'm...

284
00:20:18,660 --> 00:20:19,990
not asking for anything.

285
00:20:22,260 --> 00:20:25,230
If there's anything I can do...

286
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:28,800
for you and Hyun Jun,

287
00:20:32,500 --> 00:20:33,800
that's enough for me.

288
00:20:49,650 --> 00:20:51,390
That's actually why
I called you here.

289
00:20:52,220 --> 00:20:53,490
That Choi Yu Na.

290
00:20:54,730 --> 00:20:57,760
Keep a close eye on her
before she causes any trouble.

291
00:20:58,630 --> 00:21:00,600
If it looks like she might go
to Park Tae Ho...

292
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:05,300
and spill everything,
stop her by any means necessary.

293
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:09,710
You didn't have to tell me that.

294
00:21:10,270 --> 00:21:11,980
I was already thinking that.

295
00:21:12,510 --> 00:21:15,480
I'm stuck in this house,
completely helpless,

296
00:21:16,980 --> 00:21:18,520
so you have to watch over him.

297
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:22,750
He may be Park Tae Ho's son,

298
00:21:25,820 --> 00:21:26,820
but...

299
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:36,770
he's your son too.

300
00:21:37,870 --> 00:21:39,440
Do whatever it takes to protect him.

301
00:21:41,970 --> 00:21:43,040
My son...

302
00:21:47,380 --> 00:21:48,780
He's my son.

303
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:52,850
Of course I will.

304
00:22:13,870 --> 00:22:17,110
- He should be here by now.
- Who's coming over this early?

305
00:22:26,750 --> 00:22:29,050
Are you two close enough
to be making him breakfast?

306
00:22:30,250 --> 00:22:32,520
Today's a big day.

307
00:22:33,260 --> 00:22:34,830
He has something important to do,

308
00:22:35,090 --> 00:22:37,030
so I wanted him
to have a hearty meal.

309
00:22:37,030 --> 00:22:39,730
From what I saw last time,
he could use the extra energy.

310
00:22:40,800 --> 00:22:42,770
I didn't want to worry.

311
00:22:43,030 --> 00:22:44,940
I'm not as weak as I look.

312
00:22:45,900 --> 00:22:46,940
Dig in.

313
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:51,740
Yes, dig in. Enjoy.

314
00:22:51,910 --> 00:22:55,980
Why are you being so nice
all of a sudden? What's going on?

315
00:22:55,980 --> 00:22:58,450
Like my sister said,
today's an important day.

316
00:22:59,280 --> 00:23:02,120
I can't be teamed up
with someone weak, right?

317
00:23:03,650 --> 00:23:06,060
I'm really not weak.
Want me to prove it?

318
00:23:06,420 --> 00:23:08,860
There. Look.

319
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:13,860
Yoon Jung, what's with your hand?

320
00:23:15,370 --> 00:23:18,670
You must catch Park Cheol Su today.

321
00:23:19,100 --> 00:23:23,670
For Dan Hui and Jin Ju's sake,
you have to succeed. All right?

322
00:23:24,070 --> 00:23:25,080
Of course.

323
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:27,510
Don't worry.

324
00:23:29,250 --> 00:23:31,750
- Don't worry...
- Gosh, you really are weak.

325
00:23:32,620 --> 00:23:34,620
- Eat up.
- Unbelievable.

326
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:35,990
- Don't worry.
- Just eat.

327
00:23:36,050 --> 00:23:37,050
Don't worry...

328
00:23:37,420 --> 00:23:38,590
Dig in already.

329
00:23:42,460 --> 00:23:44,290
What did Eunhwa Trading say?

330
00:23:44,730 --> 00:23:48,060
Any word on
whether Chloe found Park Cheol Su?

331
00:23:48,270 --> 00:23:51,500
They said no one
has been asking about him.

332
00:23:51,670 --> 00:23:54,070
Then it's probably safe to assume
she hasn't connected him...

333
00:23:54,470 --> 00:23:56,070
to Eunhwa Trading yet.

334
00:23:56,070 --> 00:23:57,070
Right.

335
00:23:58,140 --> 00:23:59,980
I don't think you need to worry.

336
00:24:00,380 --> 00:24:03,080
In any case, Park Cheol Su is fine,

337
00:24:03,380 --> 00:24:06,020
and he'll be starting
a new job today.

338
00:24:07,750 --> 00:24:09,050
A new job?

339
00:24:09,350 --> 00:24:12,090
Someone was looking
for an explosives expert,

340
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:13,290
so they connected them.

341
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:14,960
Is that so?

342
00:24:15,690 --> 00:24:18,300
Someone was looking
for an explosives expert?

343
00:24:20,360 --> 00:24:21,970
Doesn't Eunhwa Trading...

344
00:24:22,800 --> 00:24:24,400
only refer people
to Park Cheol Su...

345
00:24:25,040 --> 00:24:26,200
for that kind of work?

346
00:24:26,770 --> 00:24:27,770
Yes.

347
00:24:28,310 --> 00:24:31,470
What if Chloe wasn't asking
for Park Cheol Su,

348
00:24:31,840 --> 00:24:34,380
but for an explosives expert?

349
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:38,450
What if she's trying to meet him
behind my back?

350
00:24:40,480 --> 00:24:42,750
You know what?
I'd better check for myself.

351
00:24:43,120 --> 00:24:44,860
Let's go to Eunhwa Trading
right now.

352
00:24:47,060 --> 00:24:48,060
Come on.

353
00:24:51,660 --> 00:24:52,860
Are you going somewhere?

354
00:24:55,630 --> 00:24:57,670
I have my doubts about Chloe.

355
00:24:58,170 --> 00:24:59,400
How so?

356
00:24:59,740 --> 00:25:02,140
I think she's about to backstab me.

357
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:04,610
I don't have time.
We'll talk when I get back.

358
00:25:04,610 --> 00:25:05,840
I'm going with you.

359
00:25:05,840 --> 00:25:08,280
Myung Hui,
you don't need to get involved.

360
00:25:08,380 --> 00:25:10,050
Manager Kang, let's go.

361
00:25:10,050 --> 00:25:12,880
Yes, sir.
I'll take good care of him, ma'am.

362
00:25:12,880 --> 00:25:13,920
Later.

363
00:25:19,090 --> 00:25:22,830
What's got him in such a hurry,
and where's he going?

364
00:25:24,430 --> 00:25:29,100
Did he find out that they're meeting
Park Cheol Su at Eunhwa Trading?

365
00:25:38,410 --> 00:25:41,510
Come on.
I told you to stay in the car.

366
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:43,610
I'll walk you to the entrance.

367
00:25:44,080 --> 00:25:45,750
You're doing this for me,

368
00:25:45,750 --> 00:25:48,320
so I feel guilty
just waiting comfortably alone.

369
00:25:48,550 --> 00:25:51,390
Let her. The building's
right there anyway. Let's hurry.

370
00:25:53,490 --> 00:25:54,960
Let's go. We're going to be late.

371
00:25:55,230 --> 00:25:56,360
- Okay.
- Let's go.

372
00:26:01,870 --> 00:26:05,540
(President Kim Dan Hui)

373
00:26:08,670 --> 00:26:10,170
I hope nothing goes wrong.

374
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:12,110
(Eunhwa Trading)

375
00:26:35,870 --> 00:26:37,000
After you, sir.

376
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:38,600
All right.

377
00:26:39,740 --> 00:26:42,770
Let's find out who's asking for...

378
00:26:43,240 --> 00:26:44,340
an explosives expert.

379
00:26:51,980 --> 00:26:53,950
Just wait
till I get my hands on them.

380
00:26:55,550 --> 00:26:56,550
What's this?

381
00:26:57,620 --> 00:26:59,120
(Eunhwa Trading)

382
00:27:06,200 --> 00:27:09,270
What's this doing here?

383
00:27:10,130 --> 00:27:11,330
This...

384
00:27:11,870 --> 00:27:14,440
is a gift to symbolize our promise.

385
00:27:19,380 --> 00:27:20,980
Did Kim Myung Hui...

386
00:27:23,010 --> 00:27:26,520
You. Call Eunhwa Trading right now!

387
00:27:26,580 --> 00:27:28,450
Sorry? Right. Of course, sir.

388
00:27:32,620 --> 00:27:33,620
Give it here.

389
00:27:34,690 --> 00:27:36,230
This is Park Tae Ho.

390
00:27:36,430 --> 00:27:38,430
No one is to meet
with Park Cheol Su.

391
00:27:39,430 --> 00:27:41,230
Get him out of there now!

392
00:27:42,430 --> 00:27:44,330
- Let's hurry.
- Yes, sir.

393
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:49,210
(Eunhwa Trading)

394
00:27:52,280 --> 00:27:53,480
I'm afraid the deal is off.

395
00:27:54,510 --> 00:27:55,580
You should leave now.

396
00:27:56,080 --> 00:27:58,550
Wait. What do you mean
the deal is off?

397
00:27:58,550 --> 00:28:02,550
Hey, you can't do this
after taking our down payment.

398
00:28:11,590 --> 00:28:14,100
Here's your money back.
Please leave.

399
00:28:16,170 --> 00:28:17,730
Wait, hold on.

400
00:28:19,270 --> 00:28:22,440
Is this because
of that phone call just now?

401
00:28:22,640 --> 00:28:23,870
Who was it?

402
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:26,680
Who's trying to shut this deal down?

403
00:28:27,280 --> 00:28:28,550
Who are you people, anyway?

404
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:31,750
Tell me exactly
which assemblyman sent you.

405
00:28:31,950 --> 00:28:33,750
Why are you suddenly
acting like this?

406
00:28:33,950 --> 00:28:35,120
What's gotten into you?

407
00:28:37,990 --> 00:28:39,490
- What the...
- Get out now!

408
00:28:40,160 --> 00:28:42,390
- Get him. He's Park Cheol Su.
- Darn it.

409
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:54,440
- Over there.
- There he is.

410
00:28:56,870 --> 00:29:00,610
So you let Park Cheol Su get away?

411
00:29:01,610 --> 00:29:04,350
We chased him,
but he was incredibly fast.

412
00:29:04,410 --> 00:29:07,750
I already know how slow you are
from that false accusation case.

413
00:29:08,520 --> 00:29:09,620
But you, Woo Jin?

414
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,960
You, of all people,
should've caught him!

415
00:29:12,020 --> 00:29:13,660
I did my best, you know.

416
00:29:13,860 --> 00:29:16,390
This would've been over
if it weren't for Chairman Park.

417
00:29:17,290 --> 00:29:20,160
Why did Chairman Park show up
at Eunhwa Trading?

418
00:29:21,530 --> 00:29:23,230
I'm not exactly sure either.

419
00:29:24,100 --> 00:29:25,870
He rushed off to Eunhwa Trading,

420
00:29:25,970 --> 00:29:27,470
saying he suspected you.

421
00:29:28,740 --> 00:29:32,280
He may have been keeping
an eye on us all this time.

422
00:29:33,340 --> 00:29:34,540
What do we do now?

423
00:29:35,250 --> 00:29:38,280
He's figured out
we're looking for Park Cheol Su.

424
00:29:39,350 --> 00:29:40,520
We still have a shot.

425
00:29:42,350 --> 00:29:43,350
We do?

426
00:29:43,990 --> 00:29:47,520
Park Tae Ho will try to hide
Park Cheol Su no matter what.

427
00:29:47,760 --> 00:29:51,130
This time, we'll watch
Park Tae Ho and Manager Kang,

428
00:29:52,060 --> 00:29:54,360
and catch them the moment
they make contact with Park Cheol Su.

429
00:30:22,190 --> 00:30:23,530
As for making you acting chairman,

430
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:26,230
I'm calling that off.

431
00:30:26,630 --> 00:30:29,970
I'm thinking of returning
to the company myself.

432
00:30:30,670 --> 00:30:32,670
- Already?
- The executives insist...

433
00:30:32,870 --> 00:30:34,670
there's no need
for an acting chairman.

434
00:30:35,670 --> 00:30:37,370
They believe...

435
00:30:38,010 --> 00:30:41,540
I should be the one
to lead Adele Group.

436
00:30:43,780 --> 00:30:45,220
Myung Hui, what do you think?

437
00:30:46,780 --> 00:30:48,820
If your health isn't an issue,

438
00:30:49,420 --> 00:30:50,790
then of course you should return.

439
00:30:51,190 --> 00:30:52,860
Don't worry about my health.

440
00:30:53,460 --> 00:30:55,790
My doctor already cleared me.

441
00:30:57,030 --> 00:30:58,630
Yes, I understand.

442
00:31:00,800 --> 00:31:01,860
By the way...

443
00:31:06,500 --> 00:31:07,640
Where's your bracelet?

444
00:31:08,100 --> 00:31:09,110
Sorry?

445
00:31:12,810 --> 00:31:14,910
You were definitely wearing it
this morning.

446
00:31:15,810 --> 00:31:18,880
Did you lose it somewhere?

447
00:31:21,320 --> 00:31:23,390
I'm not sure. I'll check.

448
00:31:37,630 --> 00:31:40,900
(Marriage Registration:
Park Tae Ho, Kim Myung Hui)

449
00:31:54,150 --> 00:31:55,220
Kim Myung Hui,

450
00:31:56,850 --> 00:31:59,390
why were you at Eunhwa Trading?

451
00:32:00,420 --> 00:32:01,860
I promised you marriage...

452
00:32:03,060 --> 00:32:05,500
and access to my slush fund ledger.

453
00:32:07,700 --> 00:32:09,970
Yet, you betrayed me
and conspired with Chloe.

454
00:32:10,330 --> 00:32:12,470
For what, exactly?

455
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:42,500
(Pearl in Red)

456
00:32:42,800 --> 00:32:44,800
Me, as chairman?

457
00:32:44,830 --> 00:32:46,570
Isn't this a great opportunity?

458
00:32:46,570 --> 00:32:48,910
Please don't take
too long to decide.

459
00:32:49,310 --> 00:32:51,070
Why do I feel so useless now?

460
00:32:51,070 --> 00:32:52,410
Have you changed,

461
00:32:52,410 --> 00:32:54,880
or am I the one who's changed
now that I'm not...

462
00:32:54,880 --> 00:32:56,150
Park Tae Ho's son anymore?

463
00:32:57,180 --> 00:32:59,250
Sir, we've got a problem!
You have to leave immediately.

464
00:32:59,250 --> 00:33:00,280
Park Tae Ho,

465
00:33:00,280 --> 00:33:02,320
you're under emergency arrest
for ordering...

466
00:33:02,390 --> 00:33:04,120
the manufacture
and use of explosives.

467
00:33:04,350 --> 00:33:06,720
What? An emergency arrest?

468
00:33:07,990 --> 00:33:09,990
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
